- 维度定义：[`page-horizontal-quality-spec.md`](specs/feature-tree/runtime/runtime-client-foundation/page-horizontal-quality-spec.md)  
- L3 索引：[`page-horizontal-quality/spec.md`](specs/feature-tree/runtime/runtime-client-foundation/page-horizontal-quality/spec.md)  
